I'm not sure about the organic parts. Soundwave had all his outer armor 
removed if Scattershot did turn him into a suit, so alot of his organic parts 
are probably gone.

::Dark One::

Walking out of the Alliance base, Dark One transforms into vehicle mode, 
flying off toward the battle.

He scans his internal systems as he flies, checking for any damage that he 
didn't know about.
